item.title: CVE-2023-22883|2023-03-16T00:00:00 -- zoom%20video%20communications%20inc -- zoom%20client%20for%20meetings%20for%20it%20admin%20windows%20installers
item.description: Zoom Client for IT Admin Windows installers before version 5.13.5 contain a local privilege escalation vulnerability. A local low-privileged user could exploit this vulnerability in an attack chain during the installation process to escalate their privileges to the SYSTEM user.
